 archetypischer Personenprofile, basierend auf umfangreichen Befragungen, wurde im Projekt Sireva (FKZ: 13N12954) erprobt und evaluiert.</p>", "              </div></div></section><section aria-labelledby=\"author-information\" data-title=\"Author information\"><div class=\"c-article-section\" id=\"author-information-section\"><h2 class=\"c-article-section__title js-section-title js-c-reading-companion-sections-item\" id=\"author-information\">Author information</h2><div class=\"c-article-section__content\" id=\"author-information-content\"><h3 class=\"c-article__sub-heading\" id=\"affiliations\">Affiliations</h3><ol class=\"c-article-author-affiliation__list\"><li id=\"Aff1\"><p class=\"c-article-author-affiliation__address\">Lehrstuhl und Institut f\u00fcr Arbeitswissenschaft, RWTH Aachen, Bergdriesch\u00a027, 52062, Aachen, Deutschland</p><p class=\"c-article-author-affiliation__authors-list\">Katharina Sch\u00e4fer M.A.,\u00a0 Alexander Mertens,\u00a0Peter Rasche M.Sc.,\u00a0Sabine Theis M.Sc.,\u00a0Christina Br\u00f6hl M.Sc.,\u00a0Olga Apdarmani B.Sc.,\u00a0Tobias Seinsch B.Sc.,\u00a0 Verena Nitsch,\u00a0 Christopher Brandl\u00a0&amp;\u00a0 Matthias Wille</p></li></ol><div class=\"u-js-hide u-hide-print\" data-test=\"author-info\"><span class=\"c-article__sub-heading\">Authors</span><ol class=\"c-article-authors-search u-list-reset\"><li id=\"auth-Katharina-Sch_fer\"><span class=\"c-article-authors-search__title u-h3 js-search-name\">Katharina Sch\u00e4fer M.A.</span><div class=\"c-article-authors-search__list\"><div class=\"c-article-authors-search__item c-article-authors-search__list-item--left\"><a href=\"/search?dc.creator=&#34;Katharina+Sch%C3%A4fer&#34;\" class=\"c-article-button\" data-track=\"click\" data-track-action=\"author link - publication\" data-track-label=\"link\">View author publications</a></div><div class=\"c-article-authors-search__item c-article-authors-search__list-item--right\"><p class=\"search-in-title-js c-article-authors-search__text